{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 5}
We'd sit across the street on [G7]the depot porch 
Looking at the folks looking [C]back at us
Munching on a dust covered [F]ice cream cone 
And [G7]wondering how we'd get back [C]home
{end_of_verse}

